<group name="vlan_id_vlan_name_status_interfaces">
{{VLAN_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{VLAN_NAME}} {{STATUS | ORPHRASE}} {{INTERFACES | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="vlan_id_vlan_name_status">
{{VLAN_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{VLAN_NAME}} {{STATUS | ORPHRASE}}

cli_content:
VLAN  Name                             Status    Ports
----- -------------------------------- --------- -------------------------------
1     default                          active    Et1
10    Test1                            active    Et1, Et2
20    Test2                            suspended
30    VLAN0030                         suspended
